<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>blog.y2kbugger.com - workshop</title><link href="http://blog.y2kbugger.com/" rel="alternate"/><link href="http://blog.y2kbugger.com/feeds/workshop.atom.xml" rel="self"/><id>http://blog.y2kbugger.com/</id><updated>2026-05-11T00:00:00-04:00</updated><entry><title>Steel Tanker Desk Restoration</title><link href="http://blog.y2kbugger.com/steel-tanker-desk.html" rel="alternate"/><published>2018-10-08T23:09:30-04:00</published><updated>2026-05-11T00:00:00-04:00</updated><author><name>zak kohler</name></author><id>tag:blog.y2kbugger.com,2018-10-08:/steel-tanker-desk.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;A low-text photo log of restoring a steel tanker desk and matching file cabinet, from teardown to final assembly.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/finished-desk-with-chair-and-file-cabinet.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Finished desk and file cabinet&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Finished desk and file cabinet.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="my-grandfathers-desk"&gt;My grandfathers desk&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inherited my grandfather's steel tanker desk, and found a General Fireproofing file cabinet to match.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-before-restoration-in-workshop.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk before restoration in workshop&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk before restoration in workshop.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/cabinet-interior-before-restoration.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Initial teardown before moving&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Initial teardown before moving.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-disassembled-parts-in-room.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk disassembled parts in room&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk disassembled parts in room.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-loading-into-car-trunk.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk loaded into the trunk&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk loaded into the trunk.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-and-panels-on-car.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk and cabinet after pickup&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk and cabinet after pickup.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="tear-down"&gt;Tear-down&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The starting point was solid but rough, with rust, dirt, and worn paint all over the working parts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/worn-mounting-bolt-closeup.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Worn mounting bolt closeup&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Worn mounting bolt closeup.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/lead-test-kit.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Lead test kit&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Lead test kit.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The lead test took about 24 hours to develop, which points toward a chromate-based lead yellow rather than a quicker-reacting pigment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/grandfathers-die-found-within.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Grandfathers die found within&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Grandfathers die found within.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I put my grandfather's die back inside as an easter egg for whoever is next to disassemble it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="prep"&gt;Prep&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once the desk was apart, the job became cleaning, sorting hardware, and getting every panel ready for paint.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/sorted-hardware-bags.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Sorted hardware bags&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Sorted hardware bags.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/stripped-desk-parts-on-movers-blanket.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Cleaned parts staged for paint&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Cleaned parts staged for paint.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/door-panels-ready-for-paint.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Door panels ready for paint&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Door panels ready for paint.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/linoleum-desktop.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Linoleum desktop&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Linoleum desktop.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/steel-age-nameplate-closeup.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Steel age nameplate closeup&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Steel age nameplate closeup.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/masked-nameplate-before-paint.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Masked nameplate before paint&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Masked nameplate before paint.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/shoe-covers-and-paint-can.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Shoe covers and paint can&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Shoe covers and paint can.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/respirator-selfie-4.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Respirator selfie 4&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Respirator selfie 4.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="paint"&gt;Paint&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The blue frame color and gray panels brought it back fast once the pieces were clean and ready for paint.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/garage-paint-booth-wide.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Garage paint booth wide&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Garage paint booth wide.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/painted-parts-hanging-in-garage.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Painted parts hanging in garage&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Painted parts hanging in garage.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/primed-cabinet-shell.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Cabinet shell in primer&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Cabinet shell in primer.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/painted-desk-body-in-garage.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Freshly painted cabinet shell&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Freshly painted cabinet shell.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/painted-desktop-underside.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Painted desktop underside&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Painted desktop underside.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="reassembly"&gt;Reassembly&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once the paint was done, the desk started to come back together in stages, beginning with the cabinet and working back toward the sliding parts and locks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/finished-file-cabinet.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Finished file cabinet&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Finished file cabinet.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-top-and-side-panels-fit-check.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk top and side panels fit check&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk top and side panels fit check.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/typewriter-shelf-installed.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Typewriter shelf installed&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Typewriter shelf installed.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/typewriter-shelf-installed-2.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk reassembled with the typewriter shelf&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk reassembled with the typewriter shelf.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/drawer-shelf-installed.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Drawer shelf installed&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Drawer shelf installed.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/typewrite-body-partially-reassembled.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Typewrite body partially reassembled&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Typewrite body partially reassembled.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-during-final-assembly.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk during final assembly&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk during final assembly.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/desk-lock-closeup-3.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Desk lock closeup 3&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Desk lock closeup 3.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/door-latch-closeup.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Door latch closeup&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Door latch closeup.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="finished"&gt;Finished&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The finished set keeps the industrial look but feels a lot less tired than when it came home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/finished-desk-and-file-cabinet.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Finished desk and file cabinet&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Finished desk and file cabinet.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/finished-desk-front.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Finished desk&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Finished desk.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/finished-desk-open-drawer-and-door.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Open left cabinet and typewriter shelf&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Open left cabinet and typewriter shelf.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src="../img/steel-tanker-desk/finished-desk-with-chair-and-file-cabinet.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;Finished desk with chair and file cabinet&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Finished desk with chair and file cabinet.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="workshop"/><category term="finishing"/><category term="metalwork"/><category term="restoration"/></entry></feed>